---
title: Crispy Chicken Thighs with Roasted Radishes, Carrots, and Summer Herb Gremolata
description: Roasting radishes and carrots transforms them from crisp and crunchy to tender and mellow. To make life easier, our summer herb gremolata serves double duty as both a condiment for crispy-skinned chicken and as a salad dressing flavour-booster.
